script:
1). Did you know about our money back guarantee?
I'll come back tomorrow.
No, I'm afraid I didn't. 
Yes, I'll put money in the bank.
2). Why did Mr. Walters move his desk?
He wanted a better view. 
Yes, he just got a new one.
He moved it to another room down the hall.
3). Are you the new accountant from the head office?
No, my new one came from the marketing office.
Our partner designed these patterns for us.
Yes. I'm here to assist for a few months.
